content.detailedDescription:
As i was lying in our living room at around 12 noon i noticed from our glass window a single flying object in the blue sky. the object is silvery white elongated and looks like an airplane far above. as i watch i’m a little bit wondering because in our province plane does not usually pass and extremely rare as there is no airport nearby. i estimated that the height level of the object is for jet plane, however this “jet plane” does not have smoke trail. jet planes sighting is the more common occurrence in our place. my curiosity is more heightened when i noticed that it barely moves, planes or jet planes can be out of sight in seconds or few minutes. but this object is already over 5 minutes in my line of sight and still there. 
i called my 8 year old son to show it, but my son is playing and it takes another few minutes before he came out. when he came out i show him the direction of the object. he’s having difficulty in seeing it so i stand up and open our glass sliding door to show it better.
but to my amazement the object is not alone but trailing it are more flying objects vertically spread that when i counted there are at least twenty five (25) similar flying objects. i’m already so excited at this moment that i called my son’s nanny and also some workers in my neighbour and they too see the flying objects. similar to the first one all the flying object are just slowly moving (right to left) like in a squadron formation. then they are almost stationary in front of me above. i watch it continuously thinking that maybe they would scatter in different directions. but they just all fade away farther more in the sky.
i have taken a video in my phone camera, but the small object is not visible when i replay.
after a few minutes of disappearance, clouds suddenly covered the blue sky then began to rain and few minutes the blue sky is back. i thought maybe their cover is a bit late.
content.summary: At least 25 silvery white unknown flying object observed far above in the horizon

content.detailedDescription:
I was running from the secret service (men in black) problems at fort knox or maybe the big p. not sure but i was racing faster through a field when a very disturbing loud screeching noise hovered above me. a flashlight came down surrounding me. i was paralized looking down at the grass. it faded to black as i passed out.

when i woke im not dumb as i knew i was in a metal room with strange built in luminating lighting in the ceiling. i did realize a presence and a deep telekinetic voice entered my head saying how surprised they are to learn that im able to withstand the amount of pressure surrounding me whilst moving at great speed through space.

anyway he assured me no harm and said no we do not eat your kind as we dont have mouths, only eyes and nostrils. he told me it is safe to get up and stand. oh boy it was like being on the gravatron machine or even pluto. i had to heave my body to my side and force myself off the unit bed to stand up. you can look at me he said and said it will take time to walk properly and then i looked and for the very first time in this lifetime, i observed a tall creature man. most definately scary but assured me again there is no danger and that he already knew i had a 1001 questions including god.He was so skinny-thin with long arms and two and a half fingers. two small nostrils almost built in with no mouth

he said to follow him towards the captains room,but not to touch the walls like star trek and there was another they are the same. anyway to cut a two year journey short it was so amazing and they taught me so much on our endeavor throughout a colorful and full of light journey with
places in space and other areas with planets and landing spots. i learned to drive but not land or take off at least i was privileged to navigate through space at a speed and directions too fast to understand. and i earned my stay as a worthy friend and operator.

coming home:
on my return i never forgot that day my good friends and only family companions said it would be sad how they can not interfere with the nature of human relations as i was lucky.
we landed and i did not want to leave them but that was my gift from them plus i was kinda homesick. i walked through the door so happy very very happy to see my family and you know what? they were looking like they saw a ghost i was wondering what they were looking at? then there was silence...And they all started at the same time is it you? is that really you? we thought you were dead! 

. okay now that sideways look.

they found it very extremely hard believe me but you know what i found to be extremely harder?

they said i was gone for a long time
yes i was presumed long gone
and you know what i mean?

okay thats my touch base story with you all and now i really need a coffee. i dont have much to go by but i am a good sketcher it helps me remember.
content.summary: Dark disc round-irritating screech noise-flashing lights with strong powerful beam light coming down-watch the grass fade to black-fell asleep inb the pulsating heat of the light as the hovering sound got louder-on metal bed-moving fast-vibrating-dark roo

content.detailedDescription:
Last week, i attended afcea west 2016, a conference in san diego every year. on tuesday night, i was at the gaslamp marriott rooftop bar which overlooks the convention center and coronado island. i was in a group of 5 people and 3 of us were facing coronado island when we saw an unmistakable green streak of light that looked like a shooting star except that it was green.  3 people noticed it and gave out oohs and aahhs. i high fived someone who also saw it.  

i would have concluded it was a shooting star but it was clearly low altitude and more importantly it changed direction slightly and gained altitude. 

here's a key thing: this area is restricted airspace because navy ships dock there and there is a naval air station there as well.  whatever this object was would have been both in restrictive airspace due to the navy base but also due to the airport nearby. 

i've seen shooting stars. i've seen fireworks. i've seen every type of conventional aircraft and i've seen green laser lights in the sky. this object was none of these.
content.summary: Streak of light over restricted airspace naval airbase coronado island

content.detailedDescription: Our daughter got a science set for christmas and on december 27,2015, it was warm outside so we went outside to do one of the messier experiments. it was about 3:30 when i looked up towards the sky and saw something flying towards our direction. my husband was outside with us and i told them to look at it. i asked him what it was and he was as lost as i was. it looked almost "n" shaped and a copper color but it would shift from side to side and the color and shape would change. it was almost like the sun would hit it and the color would change. we walked to the side of the yard to see it better but it started going higher and faster and that is when we noticed two more  objects in the sky only they were spaced out from the first one and farther away and looked like metallic balls. we tried to get pictures but even with the camera on action shot the photo's were impossible to get. there was no sound from anything around us, including the objects, there were a few birds but as the object got close to them the birds would scatter. they flew straight for a few minutes but started to climb and just vanished. the first one we saw, which was the closest to us, flew about 20 to 30 feet above the power lines but with the way it was moving, it was hard to get an exact color and shape. after they disappeared we just stood there for a minute asking each other what we just saw, neither of us could define to the other what the objects were, we were at a loss. the objects had no set color, other than metallic because they seemed to shine, they had no flight pattern, they left no trails, they didn't make a sound, the birds flew from them and then they climbed and just disappeared. we are still curious as to what we saw, it was a very confusing 4 minutes.
content.summary: We were outside with our daughter working on a scince kit she got for christmas when 3 obkects flew over head.

content.detailedDescription: Looked like a star ,that large ,and hauling butt!  2 at night .
content.summary: So fast , skipped left to right like rock on water .

content.detailedDescription: My friend warren and i were at his house watching tv on the morning of february 20th. heard some noises that sounded like someone walking around on the hard snow outside. we looked out his balcony window and noticed movement in the treeline on the back of the property. it was around 3:30am. we watched for about 15-20 minutes and we assumed it was just an animal so we waited to see if it was a deer, fox etc. the figure was about 75-100 yards away. we couldnt identify what kind of animal it was and we closed the blinds and went back to watching tv. moments later we heard more noises and when we looked outside again there were several figures slowly moving around. we couldnt tell exactly how many were there or exactly what they were doing. we got a flashlight and shined it at the figures and thats when we saw that they were approximately 4-5 feet tall and all appeared to be the same size and they were walking around on two legs. it was very dark and far enough away that we honestly couldn't make out faces or clothing or anything. we thought the figures could be kids messing around or something so we went out with his dog to see what was going on. by the time we walked through his house and down his stairs and got outside the figures were nowhere to be seen. his dog was acting very weird and when we went over to the area where the "people" were walking around there were no tracks or any signs of movement in the snow. we both assured ourselves that we were not crazy and that we both definitely seen something out there. we went back inside and within minutes starting hearing strange noises outside again. we opened his curtains and sure as shit there was figures walking around again in the same area. the dog was acting very weird and putting her tail between her legs and whining. i shined the flashlight at the area and yelled "what do you want." no noise or response was heard. we then heard noises on the side of the house. we were standing right next to each other and we shined the flashlight in the tree beside his house and there was a creature with a large head in the tree looking out towards the figures moving around in the treeline. the creature turned his head toward us and looked directly at us. it had an unusually large head and eyes. the level of fear that came over me was unlike anything i have ever felt in my life. i have goosebumps covering my body this moment thinking about it. we both were scared half to death. we closed the curtains and when we finally regained the courage to open them again minutes later the creature in the tree was gone and the figures in the distance were also gone. between the weird stuff that was happening in the area recently and what we saw in that tree, and the lights that were above the area when i left hours later i am convinced that what we witnessed was either not from this world or proof to me that demons actually exist. i have had a weird intermittent ringing in my ear ever since that night. he contacted me last night and said that he was having electrical interference issues. we believe we had a close encounter with entities not from our everyday world. i know what we saw the other night  was real and nobody can convince me otherwise no matter how crazy it sounds. my brother asked me if we were drunk or on some sort of drugs and i told him we were both stone cold sober and he just laughed it off. i really dont care if anyone believes us or if they think we are crazy because the level of fear i had that night and still get from thinking about it assures me it was real. i just thought someone else would be interested in our experience or could maybe explain to us what they were or could be
content.summary: Friend and i noticed movement in treeline on property late morning. looked in tree next to house and both seen an unknown being observing us

content.detailedDescription:
I was hiking in the hocking hills in southern ohio on an unusually warm day on 2/20/2016. my exact coordinates were (39°24'21.3"n 82°31'50.4"w) the sky was completely clear and the temperature was around 60 degrees.

while hiking i decided to take photos of a fire tower up on one of the the trails at the highest elevation in the park. the fire tower is 998' tall. the sun was lower and to the west, and was blinding my vision and i believe that at the time i was facing south. i figured my camera phone would be able to take pictures of the fire tower, so i blindly aimed it at the tower and snapped a series of 8 photos. the photos were taken between 3:16 pm and 3:17 pm in rapid succession. at no point in taking the photos did i see any objects in the sky.

after examining the photos at home, i noticed that i captured some sort of object, first appearing faintly and then coming what seemed to be closer and into better vision and focus. i can only make guesses as to the motion and speed of the object, but each photo was taken in a one minute span so it appears that the object was moving rapidly. after looking through the photos in succession, it does appear that the object was descending from the sky at first, and then in the last few photos, it remained in the same spot.

the object is hard to make out at first, but then comes into much better view and focus in the last pictures. the object appears to be reflecting the sunlight, and the shape of the object seemed to be either round or what looks like very faintly a triangle.

at no point during the encounter did i remember hearing any noise from the craft. i spoke to no one else about it either on the trail because at the time i didn't even realize that i had witnessed it.

the uploaded photos are labeled with time stamps which is interesting because it can be compared with the location of the object. possibly someone better at figuring movement based on time would be able to approximate speed.
content.summary: Hocking hills oh ufo sighting with a series of 8 timestamped photos.

content.detailedDescription: I was triing to fall asleep in my best friends house when i noticed a light outside the window. we were about 12 years old at that time. but there's still no reasen to have doubt about what i say. i woke my friend up to show him what i saw outside. so my friend saw the object as well. the object was quiet far away, i guess, but it still seemed giant. it was about as big as the full moon. it was a cloudy night, so the object must have been extremely bright. it was clearly behind the clouds. when i first niticed the object i emidiately thought i was seeing an ufo, i hat no idea what it could be. we watched the objekt moving back and forth from w to e for about 10 minutes. than it suddenly flew away extremly fast (seemed like light velocity, as known from movies) towarts south, right across our heats. during the sighting my friend and me wondered wheather we should try to take a video but it was night and all we had at that time was a nintendo ds camara which had quiet bad quality. on the one hand we were a bit scared eventhough there was no evidence of attacs or so. on the other hand we were curious. we wanted to fnd out what we saw. we still talk about that incident often and we're still sure that we did not see an airplane or anything like that. there were no position lights, it was not moving like any known terrestrial aircraft, it was only oval, bright (not flashing) and giant. please excuse me for spelling or grammar mistakes. as you know i'm from germany :d
content.summary: Oval, bright light, giant. moving back and forth from w to e. later it disapeared incredably fast towards south

content.detailedDescription:
I was hiking in the hocking hills in southern ohio on an unusually warm day on 2/20/2016. my exact coordinates were (39°24'21.3"n 82°31'50.4"w) the sky was completely clear and the temperature was around 60 degrees.

while hiking i decided to take photos of a fire tower up on one of the the trails at the highest elevation in the park. the fire tower is 998' tall. the sun was lower and to the west, and was blinding my vision and i believe that at the time i was facing south. i figured my camera phone would be able to take pictures of the fire tower, so i blindly aimed it at the tower and snapped a series of 8 photos. the photos were taken between 3:16 pm and 3:17 pm in rapid succession. at no point in taking the photos did i see any objects in the sky.

after examining the photos at home, i noticed that i captured some sort of object, first appearing faintly and then coming what seemed to be closer and into better vision and focus. i can only make guesses as to the motion and speed of the object, but each photo was taken in a one minute span so it appears that the object was moving rapidly. after looking through the photos in succession, it does appear that the object was descending from the sky at first, and then in the last few photos, it remained in the same spot.

the object is hard to make out at first, but then comes into much better view and focus in the last pictures. the object appears to be reflecting the sunlight, and the shape of the object seemed to be either round or what looks like very faintly a triangle.

at no point during the encounter did i remember hearing any noise from the craft. i spoke to no one else about it either on the trail because at the time i didn't even realize that i had witnessed it.

the uploaded photos are labeled with time stamps which is interesting because it can be compared with the location of the object. possibly someone better at figuring movement based on time would be able to approximate speed.
content.summary: Hocking hills oh ufo sighting with a series of 8 timestamped photos.

content.detailedDescription:
In the afternoon i noticed an interesting cloud formation.  i love photographing weather and snapped an image with my iphone 6.  not thinking anything of it, i moved the image to my computer and zoomed in to see the could formation.  in the lower right corner, upon an extensive zoom on the image, there is a very apparent metallic object which appears to be near the clouds.

unfortunately the object is very pixilated.  i do not have any software to enhance the image but i thought this event is worth mentioning.

to see the object, keep focus on the lower right corner of the image just above the tree in the lower right corner.  not visible on the image until a zoom is applied...

thanks!
content.summary: I photographed clouds and discovered a ufo in the image

content.detailedDescription: I was in my house and passed by my window when i thought i saw the white light of an airplane above the houses behind me, however, it moved erratically.  it was a simple white dot, bigger than a star. it disappeared for 30 seconds and came back, but bigger/closer this time, so i went outside and noticed that it now had a red light on top and i heard a whirring noise.  i assumed it was a drone toy of some sort, but it happened so fast that i could not determine the actual size and distance of the object.  when it "saw" me, it appeared to descend quickly and disappear. this object was shaped like a stereo typical ufo - disk shaped with a small dome/light on top.  it could have been a toy, but after some pondering, i decided it might be worth reporting just in case.
content.summary: Drone like object with white and red lights

content.detailedDescription:
Last summer i was visiting a friend's home in lake hopatcong, nj for a reunion with some of our college friends.  it was about 4 o'clock in the afternoon when our host offered to take us out for a ride on their pontoon boat.  

clouds began to form fairly quickly as i recall. within minutes it seemed. i was taking pictures all the time when i noticed this v-shaped cloud which i found odd but beautiful. i took pictures of the cloud formation within a few seconds of each other because the boat was rocking a bit from the wakes of other boats.  we figured we should return before getting caught in the rain. we got back just in time and it began to pour. it lasted maybe 10 minutes then it stopped. all clear after that.

i did not notice until the next day when i was looking at my pictures of our fun-filled day that there was an object in one of the series of pics i took of the clouds. 

when i expanded it it seemed to me instantly to be an unidentified object.  not a bird, a plane or other typical object you would find in the sky. i could see what looked like exhaust or a short contrail too.  i showed this to many folks. most dismissed it as a ufo that it must be "something else,"  or, "it's probably a bird" and "i don't know what that is."

i have debated for months whether i should share it. not saying this is from another world, but i don't know what it is.
content.summary: I discovered this after taking picture.  i did not see it as it happened. shortly thereafter a torrential rain storm. no thunder or lightning.

content.detailedDescription: My boyfriend and i were coming from buck hill rd in pascoag, ri. we were driving down putnam pike around between 5-7pm, i saw what looked like a plane with tiny blue and purple lights for some reason it caught my attention and told my boyfriend to look. then we saw what appeared to be 4 somewhat large circular lights at the bottom 2 purple and 2 blue. my boyfriend went to turn around because we couldn't believe our eyes and it was gone and no where in the sky to be found. a few mins later we continued down the road and we saw what looked like the same purple and blue lights but it looked like it was very distant and looked like a large flashing star in the sky. before we first saw what we think was a ufo both our phones died completely and our car charger refused to work until about 30 mins later after leaving pascoag
content.summary: 4 circle lights 2 blue 2 purple

content.detailedDescription:
My daughter looked up and observed a huge ball of light in the night sky, over the hawaii marine base where she lives w/her husband. (whom is military police.) she watched for a bit, as it was so much bigger and brighter than everything else in the sky. thats when it started pulsing and moving around.  it would get dimm, then extremely bright over and over as it maneuvered around.  she realized it was much closer. maybe a mile away in the sky. she then became amazed so she called a friend (neighbor)and the cell phones went to static. when her friend walked over, she began observing the object as well. after apx 15 mind. or so....It went off and was gone. immediately the entire island lost all power.Then....They witnessed aircraft that seemed to be circling the surrounding areas. no one has explained what happened yet. so she's a bit un-nerved but excited. so she calls me and tells me her story because she knows i would believe her. (as we saw a similar event happen in nc (near monroe)back in 2008 that she witnessed with me. she then confides that she saw something similar about 3- months ago. then again about 3- nights ago. now this. so she is now a bit more concerned of what it could be and what is going on. she is surrounded by military and definitely knows what those aircraft look and sound like. this was not an aircraft she is familiar with. considering it also had no sounds!  she wanted me to report it as she is worried about her military connection. however she is willing to talk to someone.
her phone number is (386)-299-5518 and please be discreet as she is a little hesitant for above said reasons. though... we both feel these occurrences need reported and investigated. we are wondering if anyone else reported it. it seems many, many, observed it but are too reluctant to report it. also, because of their military connections. 
we are fans of james fox and his work at mufon so we are hoping it is taken seriously.  thank you for your time, and listening. 😃 
 (daughter's name is chelsey)
